title: QLS Classic: Dyana Williams
itunes:title: QLS Classic: Dyana Williams
description:
Godmother of Black music, Dyana Williams, talks growing up in the Bronx, getting her start in radio as Ebony Moonbeams and coaching artists like Kanye, Lil' Kim and Dave Matthews Band.
